## Development Guidelines

### Code Standards
- Follow platform-specific best practices
- Implement proper error handling for hardware interactions
- Write modular, testable code
- Document hardware requirements and setup
- Use version control for all code and configurations

### IoT & Edge Computing Best Practices
- Implement offline-first architecture
- Optimize for low-power consumption
- Handle intermittent connectivity
- Implement secure device authentication
- Use efficient data compression
- Implement OTA (Over-The-Air) updates
- Monitor device health and metrics

### AR/VR Development
- Optimize for 60+ FPS performance
- Implement proper spatial tracking
- Handle device capabilities gracefully
- Optimize 3D models and textures
- Implement proper lighting and shadows
- Test on target devices
- Consider user comfort and motion sickness

### Blockchain Integration
- Implement proper wallet integration
- Handle gas fees and transaction failures
- Validate smart contract interactions
- Implement proper error handling
- Use testnet for development
- Audit smart contracts before deployment
- Implement proper key management

### Project Structure (IoT)
```
project-name/
├── src/
│   ├── devices/        # Device-specific code
│   ├── edge/           # Edge computing logic
│   ├── cloud/          # Cloud integration
│   ├── ml/             # ML models
│   ├── protocols/      # Communication protocols
│   └── utils/          # Helper functions
├── models/             # ML models
├── config/             # Device configurations
└── tests/              # Test files
```

### Project Structure (AR/VR)
```
project-name/
├── src/
│   ├── scenes/         # VR/AR scenes
│   ├── components/     # 3D components
│   ├── controllers/    # Input controllers
│   ├── ai/             # AI integration
│   └── utils/          # Helper functions
├── assets/             # 3D models, textures
├── shaders/            # Custom shaders
└── tests/              # Test files
```

### Project Structure (Blockchain)
```
project-name/
├── contracts/          # Smart contracts
├── scripts/            # Deployment scripts
├── test/               # Contract tests
├── frontend/           # Web3 frontend
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── components/
│   │   ├── hooks/      # Web3 hooks
│   │   └── utils/
└── hardhat.config.js
```

