## Getting Started

### IoT Projects
```bash
cd <project-folder>
npm install
# Configure device settings
cp config.example.json config.json
# Deploy to device
npm run deploy
```

### AR/VR Projects
```bash
cd <project-folder>
npm install
npm run dev
# Open in VR headset or AR-capable device
```

### Blockchain Projects
```bash
cd <project-folder>
npm install
# Compile contracts
npx hardhat compile
# Run tests
npx hardhat test
# Deploy to testnet
npx hardhat run scripts/deploy.js --network goerli
```

